OL,5, Women should be offered talking therapy
OL,6, instead of, or as well as, hormone     
OL,7, replacement therapy (HRT) for          
OL,8, problematic menopause symptoms, new    
OL,9, draft guidance for the NHS says.       
OL,11,FThe advice - the first update in almost
OL,12,Fa decade - says cognitive behaviour    
OL,13,Ftherapy (CBT) can help with hot        
OL,14,Fflushes, and sleep and mood changes.   
OL,16,FHealth watchdog The National Institute 
OL,17,Ffor Health and Care Excellence (NICE)  
OL,18,Fsays this will give women more choice. 
OL,20,FBut critics called it "disappointing". 
